<h1 id="overview">Overview</h1>
<h3 style="font-size: 25px">
  Slayer is an exciting top-down isometric roguelike game that immerses players in a world of strategic combat and character progression. Choose from three distinct classesâ€”Mage, Barbarian, and Rogueâ€”and embark on thrilling adventures, battling fierce enemies and mastering powerful abilities.
</h3>
